OL,3,CDriver who admitted killing two girls
OL,4,Cin crash 'was told to slow down'
OL,6,FA court has heard that a speeding
OL,7,Fdriver who admitted killing two
OL,8,Fteenagers on their way to a school
OL,9,Fformal was told to slow down.
OL,11,FAnthony McGinn admitted causing the
OL,12,Fdeaths of 17-year-old Kiea McCann and
OL,13,F16-year-old Dlava Mohammed.
OL,15,FThere were emotional scenes in court
OL,16,Fon Wednesday and at times proceedings
OL,17,Fhad to break while footage of the
OL,18,Fmoment McGinn's car hit a tree in 2023
OL,19,Fwas shown.
