OL,3,CDriver who admitted killing two girls
OL,4,Cin crash 'was told to slow down'
OL,6,FAnthony McGinn was speeding when his
OL,7,FBMW lost control and hit a tree at
OL,8,Fover 70mph, killing best friends Kiea
OL,9,FMcCann and Dlava Mohammed in July 2023.
OL,11,FThe girls were getting a lift to their
OL,12,Fschool formal.
OL,14,FDlava's sister also suffered
OL,15,Fcatastrophic injuries, including brain
OL,16,Ftrauma.
