OL,3,CDriver who admitted killing two girls
OL,4,Cin crash 'was told to slow down'
OL,6,FDuring the victim impact statements,
OL,7,FDlava's father described the pain of
OL,8,Fhaving to bury his daughter, how she
OL,9,Fwas his blood, a piece of his heart,
OL,10,Fand how Dlava's mother is not the same
OL,11,Fperson.
OL,13,FShe wakes up every day with a broken
OL,14,Fheart.
OL,16,FDlava's sister who was seriously
OL,17,Finjured in the crash described feeling
OL,18,Fguilty and responsible because she
OL,19,Finvited Dlava to the dance with her.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
