OL,3,CDriver who admitted killing two girls
OL,4,Cin crash 'was told to slow down'
OL,6,FShe says her best friend and sister
OL,7,Fdied, but she survived. She's no
OL,8,Flonger the same person and never will
OL,9,Fbe.
OL,11,FKiea McCann's father described Kiea as
OL,12,Ffull of life, full of energy and full
OL,13,Fof dreams, how she wanted to become a
OL,14,Fsocial worker and help disadvantaged
OL,15,Fchildren.
OL,17,FHe says his daughter's loss has been a
OL,18,Fdeath sentence on the whole family.
