OL,3,CDriver who admitted killing two girls
OL,4,Cin crash 'was told to slow down'
OL,6,FDistressing dashcam footage of the
OL,7,Fmoment the car hit the tree was also
OL,8,Fshown in court. Some family members
OL,9,Fdidn't watch, others gasped in shock
OL,10,Fand broke down in tears, including
OL,11,FDlava's mother.
OL,13,FThe court heard the 61-year-old of
OL,14,FDrumloo, Newbliss, was a family friend
OL,15,Fof the McCanns.
OL,17,FHe'd offered to act as a chauffeur and
OL,18,Fwas trusted to take the girls to their
OL,19,Fdance.
