OL,3,CDriver who admitted killing two girls
OL,4,Cin crash 'was told to slow down'
OL,6,FThe prosecution described how Kiea's
OL,7,Fboyfriend was in the front seats of
OL,8,Fthe BMW. He told police after the
OL,9,Fcollision McGinn was speeding and he
OL,10,Fhad asked him to slow down.
OL,12,FHe looked at Kiea and she seemed
OL,13,Fscared, and seconds before the crash,
OL,14,Fhe said goodbye to her.
OL,16,FAt that point, Kia's father became
OL,17,Fvery upset, stood up in court, and
OL,18,Fshouted at McGinn, "I'll never forget
OL,19,Fyou".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
