OL,3,CDriver who admitted killing two girls
OL,4,Cin crash 'was told to slow down'
OL,6,FThe court heard McGinn was airlifted
OL,7,Fto the Royal Victoria Hospital in
OL,8,FBelfast and was in a coma for eight
OL,9,Fweeks.
OL,11,FThrough his legal team, Anthony McGinn
OL,12,Fformally apologized in court to the
OL,13,Fvictims, family and friends.
OL,15,FThe judge was told he fully accepts
OL,16,Fthe distress and damage caused, and he
OL,17,Facknowledges his behavior was reckless
OL,18,Fand he is genuinely remorseful.
OL,20,FSentencing was adjourned until next
OL,21,Fweek.
